  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p>- Free server hosting to up to 64 players<br>- First person & third person<br>- Realistic graphics and sounds<br>- Chat system<br>- Weapon skins<br>- Chat system <br>- Epic graphics <br>- Skins (for weapons) <br>- Customizable slots</p><br><h1>Steam Greenlight</h1><p>This game has been chosen to be Greenlit by the Steam community, enjoy playing!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Description</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546660/extras/0183e66487d6958d887d407110fc1e6f.webp?t=1517955855\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br>Operation Breakout is a renewed multiplayer shooter that's provided to you by SGTTB.<br>In this fantastic shooter you'll need to bundle strategy, skills and reaction rate to get to the absolute top!<br>The great textures, realistic sound effects and exciting events make the game everything but boring!<br>Explore and create own strategies to help you win this war. This is NO Pay2Win!<br><br><strong>Game Servers</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546660/extras/0183e66487d6958d887d407110fc1e6f.webp?t=1517955855\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br>Hosting servers in Operation Breakout is 100% free!<br>Creating servers will be done automaticly on one of the connected PC's and will be exited automaticly aswell.<br>No costs and easy to use!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Description</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546660/extras/0183e66487d6958d887d407110fc1e6f.webp?t=1517955855\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br>Operation Breakout is a renewed multiplayer shooter that's provided to you by SGTTB.<br>In this fantastic shooter you'll need to bundle strategy, skills and reaction rate to get to the absolute top!<br>The great textures, realistic sound effects and exciting events make the game everything but boring!<br>Explore and create own strategies to help you win this war. This is NO Pay2Win!<br><br><strong>Game Servers</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546660/extras/0183e66487d6958d887d407110fc1e6f.webp?t=1517955855\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br>Hosting servers in Operation Breakout is 100% free!<br>Creating servers will be done automaticly on one of the connected PC's and will be exited automaticly aswell.<br>No costs and easy to use!",
